Privacy Policy for MyTourGuide

Last updated: August 1, 2023

Introduction

At MyTourGuide, we respect the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully.

Collection of Your Information

We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you register for an account or use certain features of our services. This information may include your name, email address, password, and other information necessary for authentication and managing the content you have rights to.

Use of Your Information

We may use the information collected to:

Authenticate and manage your access to our services.
Respond to your inquiries and requests.
Enhance, modify, or improve our services.
Location

At MyTourGuide, we may access and use your location information only to show you where you are relative to the tour content and to enable personalized directions from your location to the tour stop content, either in the app or your deviceâ€™s map application. This information is essential for providing a tailored experience within our services.

Your location information is obtained with your explicit consent and is only used for the purposes described above. We do not share, sell, or retain this information beyond the necessary timeframe for delivering the service.

Please note that you can always modify your location settings within your device if you decide at any time that you do not want our services to access this information.

Disclosure of Your Information

We will not sell, trade, or share your information with third parties. Your information may only be disclosed to comply with legal obligations or to protect the rights, property, or personal safety of [Your Company Name], our users, or others.

Security of Your Information

We use administrative, technical, and physical security measures to protect your personal information. While we have taken reasonable steps to secure the information you provide to us, please be aware that no security measures are perfect or impenetrable, and no method of data transmission can be guaranteed against interception or other types of misuse.

Contact Us

If you have questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

info@mytourguide.com

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
